{"article_id":"obcc17GWrnOnhq4E","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"LISTEN TO ARTICLE 2:00","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"SHARE THIS ARTICLE","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"Share Tweet","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"Post Email","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"Brett Kavanaugh ' s prompt appointment to the Supreme Court is no longer the formality","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"it seemed just days ago .","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"Christine Blasey Ford , a research psychologist in California , has said","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"she ' s willing to testify in public","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"that Kavanaugh sexually assaulted her","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"when both were teenagers in the early 1980s .","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"Kavanaugh flatly denies the allegation .","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"But","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"now that the accusation is neither anonymous nor unsupported by documentary evidence","depth":11},{"id":13,"text":"( therapy notes from 2012 and 2013 reportedly show","depth":12},{"id":14,"text":"that Ford ' s claim of assault isn ' t new ) ,","depth":12},{"id":15,"text":"it must not be dismissed .","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"According to a senior Republican senator ,","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"the Senate Judiciary Committee will call Kavanaugh and his accuser to testify next Monday .","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"Good .","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"The vote on the nomination ,","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"originally scheduled for later this week ,","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"should be delayed","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"as long as necessary","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"for the full Senate and the public at large to judge","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"where the truth resides .","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"If , at the end of a fair and open process , the allegation appears credible ,","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"the nomination should be withdrawn .","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"Given that the alleged assault happened so long ago ,","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"some will say","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"that this is unfair to Kavanaugh .","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"The crime ,","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"if it happened ,","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"could not be prosecuted today ;","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"he was a minor at the time ;","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"and it ' s unlikely that the criminal test of \" beyond a reasonable doubt \" could be met .","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"But all this misses the point .","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"There ' s no shortage of excellent candidates for seats on the nation ' s highest court .","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"If , after a fair hearing , Kavanaugh ' s fitness looks questionable ,","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"it would be better to appoint somebody else .","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"Most Republicans would wish to speed the process along","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"- partly because , after November , their Senate majority isn ' t guaranteed .","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"They may rightfully complain","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"that the accusation should have been made and examined earlier .","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"Nonetheless , it ' s in their interests now to pause .","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"Rushing Kavanaugh on to the court under these circumstances would unleash a righteous fury","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"that would likely hurt Republicans most .","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"Far more important , it might gravely damage the court , the Senate , the White House and the nation -","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"by telling women , not for the first time ,","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"that they are second-class citizens .","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"The Senate should take as long","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"as necessary","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"to get this appointment right .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":103,"left":0,"right":102,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":102,"left":54,"right":101,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{